---
title: Steak and Brussels Sprouts Stir-Fry with Carrot, Ginger and Jasmine Rice
description: Brussels sprouts and stir-fry may sound like an unlikely pair, but trust us, it works. The addition of this cruciferous veggie adds a seasonal flair to the dish—not to mention a hefty dose of iron and vitamins A and C. Feel free to add as much or as little chili as you like. After all, you’re the chef!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steak-and-brussels-sprouts-stir-fry-ecb911b2.jpg
